{
  "name": "Monk Training",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/commodities/wood/bamboo-brown.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your martial arts training grants you greater offense, defense, and movement.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Iron Palm:</strong> <span class=\"cf0\">Choose a Melee Weapon Style when you gain this Feature. Your limbs are considered Natural Weapons that deal <strong>2</strong> Bludgeoning damage and can perform the Weapon Enhancement of the chosen Weapon Style.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Patient Defense: </strong>While you aren't wearing Armor you gain <strong>+2 PD</strong>. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Step of the Wind:</strong> You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>You gain +1 <strong>Speed</strong> and <strong>Jump</strong> <strong>Distance</strong>.</p></li><li><p>You can move a number of Spaces up to your Speed along vertical surfaces and across liquids without falling during your move.</p></li><li><p>You can use your <strong>Prime</strong> <strong>Modifier</strong> instead of <strong>Agility</strong> to determine your <strong>Jump</strong> <strong>Distance</strong> and the damage you take from Falling.</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
